%C3%A9ndice:Palabras_m%C3%A1s_frecuentes_del_espa%C3%B1ol" title="Apéndice:Palabras más frecuentes del español - Sbaeneg" lang="es" hreflang="es" class="interlanguage-link-target"><span>Español</span></a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-et mw-list-item"><a href="https://et.wiktionary.org/wiki/Vikis%C3%B5nastik:Sagedusloendid" title="Vikisõnastik:Sagedusloendid - Estoneg" lang="et" hreflang="et" class="interlanguage-link-target"><span>Eesti</span></a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-fa mw-list-item"><a href="https://fa.wiktionary.org/wiki/%D9%88%DB%8C%DA%A9%DB%8C%E2%80%8C%D9%88%D8%A7%DA%98%D9%87:%D9%81%D9%87%D8%B1%D8%B3%D8%AA%E2%80%8C%D9%87%D8%A7%DB%8C_%D8%A8%D8%B3%D8%A7%D9%85%D8%AF%DB%8C" title="ویکی‌واژه:فهرست‌های بسامدی - Perseg" lang="fa" hreflang="fa" class="interlanguage-link-target"><span>فارسی</span></a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-fr mw-list-item"><a href="https://fr.wiktionary.org/wiki/Wiktionnaire:Listes_de_fr%C3%A9quence" title="Wiktionnaire:Listes de fréquence - Ffrangeg" lang="fr" hreflang="fr" class="interlanguage-link-target"><span>Français</span></a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-ko mw-list-item"><a href="https://ko.wiktionary.org/wiki/%EB%B6%80%EB%A1%9D:%EB%B9%88%EB%8F%84%EB%B3%84_%EB%82%B1%EB%A7%90_%EB%AA%A9%EB%A1%9D" title="부록:빈도별 낱말 목록 - Coreeg" lang="ko" hreflang="ko" class="interlanguage-link-target"><span>한국어</span></a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-la mw-list-item"><a href="https://la.wiktionary.org/wiki/Victionarium:Dictiones_in_Project_Gutenberg_per_frequentiam" title="Victionarium:Dictiones in Project Gutenberg per frequentiam - Lladin" lang="la" hreflang="la" class="interlanguage-link-target"><span>Latina</span></a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-ml mw-list-item"><a href="https://ml.wiktionary.org/wiki/%E0%B4%B5%E0%B4%BF%E0%B4%95%E0%B5%8D%E0%B4%95%E0%B4%BF%E0%B4%A8%E0%B4%BF%E0%B4%98%E0%B4%A3%E0%B5%8D%E0%B4%9F%E0%B5%81:%E0%B4%8F%E0%B4%B1%E0%B5%8D%E0%B4%B1%E0%B